{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":{"id":"SitePage /posts/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通/"}},"pageContext":{"url":"/posts/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通/","relativePath":"posts/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通.md","relativeDir":"posts","base":"如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通.md","name":"如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通","frontmatter":{"title":"如何允许 Windows 7 主机与 Ubuntu 虚拟机互相 ping 通","stackbit_url_path":"posts/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通","date":"2014-05-26 03:49:00","excerpt":"","comments_count":0,"positive_reactions_count":0,"tags":["Ubuntu","Virtual Box","Windows 7"],"canonical_url":"https://be-net.azurewebsites.net/post/2014/05/26/如何允许-Windows-7-主机与-Ubuntu-虚拟机互相-ping-通","template":"post"},"html":"<h2><span style=\"color: #9b00d3;\">问题：</span></h2>\n<p>在 Windows 7 主机里的 Virtual Box 中安装了 Ubuntu，然后发现主机能够 Ping 通虚拟机，但反过来不行。</p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #9b00d3;\">解决方案：</span></h2>\n<p>在 Virtual Box 中的设置里，将网络连接方式改成 Host-only Adapter 之后就可以互相 Ping 通了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_626.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/3dbd64e340735667872593b815f4147f/fcda8/image_thumb_345.png\" srcset=\"/static/3dbd64e340735667872593b815f4147f/12f09/image_thumb_345.png 148w,\n/static/3dbd64e340735667872593b815f4147f/e4a3f/image_thumb_345.png 295w,\n/static/3dbd64e340735667872593b815f4147f/fcda8/image_thumb_345.png 590w,\n/static/3dbd64e340735667872593b815f4147f/0786c/image_thumb_345.png 663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>顺便说一句，在 Windows 的 cmd 里查看 IP 设置，命令为 ipconfig，但在 Ubuntu 中默认没有这个命令，不过可以使用 ifconfig 来查看 Ubuntu 的 IP 设置。</p>\n<pre class=\"cmd auto-wrap\">jeff@Jeff-Ubuntu:~$ ifconfig\neth0      Link encap:Ethernet  HWaddr 08:00:27:6c:3b:bc  \n          inet addr:192.168.56.101  Bcast:192.168.56.255  Mask:255.255.255.0\n          inet6 addr: fe80::a00:27ff:fe6c:3bbc/64 Scope:Link\n          UP BROADCAST RUNNING MULTICAST  MTU:1500  Metric:1\n          RX packets:32 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 frame:0\n          TX packets:53 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 carrier:0\n          collisions:0 txqueuelen:1000 \n          RX bytes:3844 (3.8 KB)  TX bytes:9924 (9.9 KB)</pre>\n<p>lo        Link encap:Local Loopback<br>\ninet addr:127.0.0.1  Mask:255.0.0.0\ninet6 addr: ::1/128 Scope:Host\nUP LOOPBACK RUNNING  MTU:65536  Metric:1\nRX packets:146 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 frame:0\nTX packets:146 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 carrier:0\ncollisions:0 txqueuelen:0\nRX bytes:396020 (396.0 KB)  TX bytes:396020 (396.0 KB)\n</pre></p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/